human nature, isn't it?

00:18:37.117 --> 00:18:38.576 position:50% align:center
[MOGANA]
What do you think?

00:18:38.660 --> 00:18:42.497 position:50% align:center
Becoming my cattle wouldn't
be the worst thing, would it?

00:18:42.580 --> 00:18:44.124 position:50% align:center
[RETTO]
What do I do?

00:18:44.207 --> 00:18:46.334 position:50% align:center
How do I help her
go back to normal?

00:18:46.418 --> 00:18:48.503 position:50% align:center
At this rate, we'll be...

00:18:48.586 --> 00:18:50.088 position:50% align:center
No, think!

00:18:50.171 --> 00:18:51.923 position:50% align:center
All this time
we've been together.

00:18:52.007 --> 00:18:53.925 position:50% align:center
Hoshino's weakness is...

00:18:55.510 --> 00:18:57.929 position:50% align:center
[RETTO]
It's not working. At all.

00:18:58.013 --> 00:18:59.097 position:50% align:center
[MOGANA gasps]

00:18:59.180 --> 00:19:01.433 position:50% align:center
[RETTO] I can't feel any
H-energy this way.

00:19:01.516 --> 00:19:03.601 position:50% align:center
Listen, one of your best points

00:19:03.685 --> 00:19:06.730 position:50% align:center
is that you always take how
beautiful you are for granted.

00:19:06.813 --> 00:19:09.107 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
Enjo, what are you saying?

00:19:09.190 --> 00:19:11.401 position:50% align:center
[RETTO] On the one hand,
you're strong and determined,

00:19:11.484 --> 00:19:13.945 position:50% align:center
and on the other,
you're soft and sensitive.

00:19:14.029 --> 00:19:17.991 position:50% align:center
You joined HXEROS even
when you didn't want to.

00:19:18.074 --> 00:19:21.578 position:50% align:center
You know. You're cute
even when you're blushing.

00:19:21.661 --> 00:19:23.329 position:50% align:center
But the best part is
occasionally getting to

00:19:23.413 --> 00:19:27.334 position:50% align:center
see you smile because I know
that's who you really are!

00:19:27.417 --> 00:19:31.171 position:50% align:center
And that's why, right now,
more than ever,

00:19:31.254 --> 00:19:32.505 position:50% align:center
I'm in love with--

00:19:32.589 --> 00:19:35.675 position:50% align:center
Seriously?!
Will you just shut up?!

00:19:35.759 --> 00:19:38.136 position:50% align:center
[panting]

00:19:38.219 --> 00:19:40.096 position:50% align:center
[RETTO]
Good, you're back.

00:19:40.180 --> 00:19:43.141 position:50% align:center
I was right. This is how
you're supposed to be.

00:19:43.224 --> 00:19:48.396 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA grunts] That was kind of
a rough way to make your point.

00:19:48.480 --> 00:19:49.981 position:50% align:center
[RETTO chuckles]

00:19:50.065 --> 00:19:51.066 position:50% align:center
[MOGANA gasps]

00:19:51.149 --> 00:19:53.234 position:50% align:center
[RETTO]
All right, it's time, Hoshino.

00:19:53.318 --> 00:19:54.652 position:50% align:center
Let's go defeat her.

00:19:54.736 --> 00:19:56.363 position:50% align:center
You and me, together!

00:19:56.446 --> 00:19:58.990 position:50% align:center
[MOGANA] How dare you
interfere with my meal.

00:19:59.074 --> 00:20:02.452 position:50% align:center
You pathetic,
insignificant livestock!

00:20:02.535 --> 00:20:05.580 position:50% align:center
I'm going to finish
you both right here!

00:20:08.750 --> 00:20:10.335 position:50% align:center
[RETTO]
This feeling...

00:20:10.418 --> 00:20:12.128 position:50% align:center
I remember it.

00:20:12.212 --> 00:20:14.047 position:50% align:center
That first day we fought.

00:20:14.130 --> 00:20:16.424 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
Yeah. Let's do this.

00:20:24.307 --> 00:20:29.896 position:50% align:center
[BOTH yell]

00:20:31.898 --> 00:20:35.443 position:50% align:center
[MOGANA] Remarkable! I've never
felt H-energy like this!

00:20:35.527 --> 00:20:37.570 position:50% align:center
I'm in love!

00:20:37.654 --> 00:20:40.448 position:50% align:center
Their fused H-energy is
more delicious than anything

00:20:40.532 --> 00:20:44.703 position:50% align:center
I've ever had before!
It's perfection!

00:20:44.786 --> 00:20:49.165 position:50% align:center
This is the H-energy source
we've been searching for!

00:20:52.669 --> 00:20:56.256 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA] Wait, so, that means
it's over, doesn't it?

00:20:56.339 --> 00:20:57.340 position:50% align:center
Our war, I mean?

00:20:57.424 --> 00:21:00.260 position:50% align:center
[RETTO]
Yeah. I'm sure it is.

00:21:00.343 --> 00:21:03.972 position:50% align:center
So, that promise you made me.
It still stands, right?

00:21:04.055 --> 00:21:05.306 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA]
Huh?

00:21:05.390 --> 00:21:07.142 position:50% align:center
[RETTO] You said that if
we defeated the Kiseichuu,

00:21:07.225 --> 00:21:10.270 position:50% align:center
you would answer my proposal.

00:21:10.353 --> 00:21:12.397 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA] That's when
I'll give you my answer.

00:21:12.480 --> 00:21:15.275 position:50% align:center
Ugh-- C'mon, dude!
At a time like this?!

00:21:15.358 --> 00:21:16.901 position:50% align:center
A time like what, Hoshino?!

00:21:16.985 --> 00:21:18.862 position:50% align:center
The reason I've been able
to make it this far is because

00:21:18.945 --> 00:21:20.905 position:50% align:center
I've leaned on that
thought for strength!

00:21:20.989 --> 00:21:23.742 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA whimpers] But!
What about all the Kiseichuu

00:21:23.825 --> 00:21:27.871 position:50% align:center
out there in other places?!
We gotta defeat them all!

00:21:27.954 --> 00:21:31.541 position:50% align:center
[sighs] Well...
Guess I can keep waiting.

00:21:34.044 --> 00:21:35.795 position:50% align:center
What are you
grinning about now?!

00:21:35.879 --> 00:21:37.964 position:50% align:center
Oh, I was just thinking that
maybe it wouldn't have been

00:21:38.048 --> 00:21:41.051 position:50% align:center
so bad if I'd gotten to see you
blush a little bit longer.

00:21:41.134 --> 00:21:46.056 position:50% align:center
[gasps] That's it! I am
so done being a hero!

00:21:46.139 --> 00:21:47.849 position:50% align:center
[sobs]

00:23:18.440 --> 00:23:21.359 position:50% align:center
[ANNO] Yeah, for a while there,
I didn't know what would happen!

00:23:21.443 --> 00:23:23.445 position:50% align:center
Thankfully, all the
charges were dropped.

00:23:23.528 --> 00:23:26.072 position:50% align:center
And HXEROS
is back together again!

00:23:26.156 --> 00:23:27.574 position:50% align:center
I can't wait!

00:23:27.657 --> 00:23:30.702 position:50% align:center
Oh, and I'll obviously have
to improve those XERO suits.

00:23:30.785 --> 00:23:32.537 position:50% align:center
--Great!
--I'd like to help!

00:23:32.620 --> 00:23:34.039 position:50% align:center
Aw, thank you so much.

00:23:34.122 --> 00:23:36.041 position:50% align:center
[ANNO]
Mm! [giggles]

00:23:37.751 --> 00:23:39.419 position:50% align:center
[MOMOKA]
Huh? What's the matter?

00:23:39.502 --> 00:23:41.463 position:50% align:center
Did someone use
all her H-energy?

00:23:41.546 --> 00:23:44.090 position:50% align:center
--Huh?! Why would you say that?!
--[MOMOKA] I knew it!

00:23:44.174 --> 00:23:46.176 position:50% align:center
Momoka, stop!
Please leave her alone!

00:23:46.259 --> 00:23:47.844 position:50% align:center
--There they go again.
--[laughs]

00:23:47.927 --> 00:23:49.179 position:50% align:center
[MOMOKA]
Did it tickle?

00:23:49.262 --> 00:23:50.430 position:50% align:center
[KIRARA] Would you cut it
out you total pervert?

00:23:50.513 --> 00:23:52.015 position:50% align:center
--What is wrong with you?!
--[RETTO chuckles]